window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Every time he dies, Ethan gains a little more power.<br> <br> Earth was chosen for Integration, but Ethan Hill knows from the second his Trial begins that the Integration is a lie. The beings giving Earth the 'honor' of access to their System Interface want something from Earthâ€”he just doesn't know what.<br> <br> Now he's trapped on an alien planet and lost in a time loop, fighting for strength and for his own humanity.<br> <br> One thing's for sure: He'll die as many times as it takes to tear it all down.<br> <br> Don't miss the start of this action-packed Progression Fantasy seemlessly merging aspects from Apocalyptic LitRPG's like He Who Fights with Monsters and Time Loop stories like Mother of Learning.</p>"; 
